Class Future

java.lang.Object
finance.Future
All Implemented Interfaces:
DirectedEdge
public class Future
extends java.lang.Object
implements DirectedEdge
This class represent a financial future. It is represented as a DirectedEdge connecting
"InceptionDate → DeliveryDate"
Author:
Guglielmo Del Sarto
